rows.value: $(identity.pronouns.singular) will boast the greatness of Triton civilization at every opportunity.
$(identity.pronouns.singular) speaks an antiquated version of common.
$(identity.pronouns.singular) has a hard time understanding sarcasm.
$(identity.pronouns.singular) is fascinated by the surface world, and can often be seen scribbling notes or drawings.
$(identity.pronouns.singular) is surprised when people don't know everything about Triton culture.
$(identity.pronouns.singular) is still struggling to understand the surface's culture.
$(identity.pronouns.singular) always knows if it's going to rain.
